Source: sfizz-pistomp
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Maintainer: pistomp <pistomp@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cmake, git, lv2-dev,
 libsndfile1-dev, libsamplerate0-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/sfztools/sfizz-ui

Package: sfizz-pistomp
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: sfizz, sfizz-lv2
Conflicts: sfizz, sfizz-lv2
Replaces: sfizz, sfizz-lv2
Description: SFZ library and LV2 plugin (minimal, headless)
 sfizz is an SFZ parser and synth C++ library and set of plugins.
 This build is a minimal headless LV2-only variant for pi-Stomp, with
 MOD Audio file type annotations for the SFZ file browser.
